2
00:00:57,240 --> 00:01:00,490
=Go Back Lover=

3
00:01:03,490 --> 00:01:06,530
(December 2017,
Fourth Year of University)

4
00:01:16,930 --> 00:01:18,970
(Lu Xingyan)

5
00:01:20,610 --> 00:01:21,860
Why do you look so pale?

6
00:01:22,820 --> 00:01:23,980
Do you feel unwell?

7
00:01:25,950 --> 00:01:27,340
It's that time of the month.

8
00:01:27,970 --> 00:01:29,030
Did you drink brown sugar water?

9
00:01:29,740 --> 00:01:30,620
If it doesn't work,

10
00:01:31,050 --> 00:01:32,260
do you want to visit the doctor?

11
00:01:33,150 --> 00:01:34,030
Lu Xingyan,

12
00:01:37,340 --> 00:01:38,510
I miss you.

13
00:01:43,340 --> 00:01:44,030
I'm here.

14
00:01:45,900 --> 00:01:46,510
I won't hang up.

15
00:01:48,260 --> 00:01:49,100
I'll be with you.

16
00:01:50,790 --> 00:01:51,670
Just lie down

17
00:01:52,650 --> 00:01:53,830
and sleep for a while, all right?

18
00:02:06,070 --> 00:02:06,700
I didn't hang up.

19
00:02:50,670 --> 00:02:53,540
Xingruo, I think
your boyfriend is downstairs.

20
00:02:53,860 --> 00:02:55,230
He seems to be calling someone.

21
00:02:55,580 --> 00:02:56,510
Is he calling you?

22
00:03:00,010 --> 00:03:02,690
(Lu Xingyan)

23
00:03:06,230 --> 00:03:07,390
Wear a jacket!

24
00:03:45,650 --> 00:03:46,350
You wear so little.

25
00:03:47,600 --> 00:03:49,670
You didn't change your shoes
and even wear a pair of socks.

26
00:03:53,020 --> 00:03:54,580
Do you want to get worse?

27
00:04:02,300 --> 00:04:02,910
Do you feel cold?

28
00:04:03,580 --> 00:04:04,230
Yes.

29
00:04:18,860 --> 00:04:19,980
Why are you here?

30
00:04:21,350 --> 00:04:22,460
You said you miss me

31
00:04:22,950 --> 00:04:24,700
so I bought the earliest flight here.

32
00:04:28,340 --> 00:04:28,990
Do you feel better?

33
00:04:30,070 --> 00:04:31,220
Do you need to visit the doctor?

34
00:04:32,660 --> 00:04:33,210
No.

35
00:04:33,700 --> 00:04:34,950
I'm fine when I see you.

36
00:04:40,220 --> 00:04:42,460
Don't be silly. I'm not a doctor.

37
00:04:44,700 --> 00:04:45,430
You are.

38
00:04:58,490 --> 00:05:04,850
=Episode 21=
(Going to you because you miss me.)

39
00:05:05,010 --> 00:05:08,130
(Year 2024)

40
00:05:08,130 --> 00:05:11,290
(Operating Theatre,
Do not enter unless being called)

41
00:05:13,010 --> 00:05:13,990
Lu Xingyan's family member.

42
00:05:13,990 --> 00:05:14,660
Me!

43
00:05:15,290 --> 00:05:16,190
The patient had an accident

44
00:05:16,190 --> 00:05:18,220
causing a rib fracture
and pleura puncture.

45
00:05:18,220 --> 00:05:19,120
He needs surgery immediately.

46
00:05:19,190 --> 00:05:20,510
We need his family's signature.

47
00:05:20,630 --> 00:05:21,190
I'll sign it.

48
00:05:22,700 --> 00:05:24,110
This is the risk notice.

49
00:05:24,260 --> 00:05:26,070
Are you the patient's wife?

50
00:05:26,070 --> 00:05:26,900
I am his girlfriend.

51
00:05:27,190 --> 00:05:27,730
Hold on.

52
00:05:28,160 --> 00:05:30,190
The surgery consent form
should be signed by a family member.

53
00:05:30,550 --> 00:05:32,750
Girlfriends are not
immediate family members in law.

54
00:05:32,750 --> 00:05:33,920
Does he have other family members?

55
00:05:34,220 --> 00:05:35,460
All of them are not around.

56
00:05:35,900 --> 00:05:36,870
His parents are abroad.

57
00:05:36,870 --> 00:05:37,750
This is an emergency.

58
00:05:37,750 --> 00:05:39,430
Can't we help them sign it?

59
00:05:39,700 --> 00:05:40,750
This is against the rules.

60
00:05:40,750 --> 00:05:41,460
Rules are fixed

61
00:05:41,460 --> 00:05:42,760
but we are flexible as humans. He...

62
00:05:43,510 --> 00:05:44,990
Doctor, this is about life and death.

63
00:05:44,990 --> 00:05:45,700
Please.

64
00:05:46,070 --> 00:05:47,820
All right. I'll inform the superior

65
00:05:47,820 --> 00:05:49,750
and apply for a green channel
for immediate surgery.

66
00:05:49,890 --> 00:05:51,830
We can wait until his parents are here
to sign the consent form.

67
00:05:52,110 --> 00:05:53,550
- Sure. Thank you.
- All right.

68
00:06:06,290 --> 00:06:14,170
(Star City People's Hospital,
Out-patient)

69
00:06:14,170 --> 00:06:15,020
(In Operation,
Operating theatre, Do not enter)

70
00:06:15,020 --> 00:06:15,660
Xingruo.

71
00:06:16,140 --> 00:06:17,020
Don't worry.

72
00:06:17,020 --> 00:06:18,070
Lu Xingyan will be fine.

73
00:06:18,920 --> 00:06:20,750
The scene of the accident
has almost been cleared.

74
00:06:20,750 --> 00:06:22,360
Xu Chengzhou and the rest
are rushing here.

75
00:06:22,510 --> 00:06:23,700
We are here. Don't worry.

76
00:06:27,610 --> 00:06:29,690
(In Operation)

77
00:06:37,550 --> 00:06:39,140
The operation is quite successful.

78
00:06:39,510 --> 00:06:40,990
The rib fracture
and pneumothorax surgery

79
00:06:40,990 --> 00:06:41,820
have been completed.

80
00:06:42,070 --> 00:06:43,580
However, his intracranial haemorrhage

81
00:06:43,580 --> 00:06:45,220
did not meet the indications
for surgical intervention.

82
00:06:45,510 --> 00:06:47,070
The patient is in a coma.

83
00:06:47,260 --> 00:06:48,630
In the next 24 hours,

84
00:06:48,870 --> 00:06:50,510
the haemorrhage might get worse.

85
00:06:51,140 --> 00:06:52,340
Are you saying

86
00:06:52,820 --> 00:06:54,310
that it might get worse for him?

87
00:06:54,660 --> 00:06:56,220
Which is why
he has to be observed closely.

88
00:06:56,460 --> 00:06:57,900
Usually, if the situation remains,

89
00:06:58,460 --> 00:07:00,260
he will wake up after a day or two.

90
00:07:00,260 --> 00:07:02,150
However, there's also a possibility
that it might get worse.

91
00:07:02,430 --> 00:07:05,260
So, we will observe his vital signs
and state of consciousness closely.

92
00:07:05,750 --> 00:07:06,630
We will also follow up

93
00:07:06,630 --> 00:07:07,360
with a brain CT scan

94
00:07:07,700 --> 00:07:09,390
to monitor the amount
of bleeding in his brain.

95
00:07:09,630 --> 00:07:10,660
If the situation gets worse,

96
00:07:10,870 --> 00:07:12,310
we will have to intervene surgically,

97
00:07:12,460 --> 00:07:13,820
which is a craniotomy.

98
00:07:19,510 --> 00:07:20,110
Lu Xingyan.

99
00:07:20,120 --> 00:07:20,970
Family members, make way.

100
00:07:21,020 --> 00:07:21,560
Xingruo.

101
00:07:26,630 --> 00:07:27,170
Xingruo.

102
00:07:31,970 --> 00:07:34,970
(In-patient Department)

103
00:07:58,580 --> 00:08:00,750
I've troubled all of you today.

104
00:08:01,430 --> 00:08:02,700
I can just stay here alone.

105
00:08:02,890 --> 00:08:04,110
All of you should go home and rest.

106
00:08:04,510 --> 00:08:05,900
I can also stay here.

107
00:08:06,480 --> 00:08:08,430
The hospital only allows one person
to stay with him.

108
00:08:08,900 --> 00:08:09,820
I should stay.

109
00:08:10,010 --> 00:08:11,190
I'll come tomorrow to replace you.

110
00:08:11,460 --> 00:08:12,950
You can't handle this alone.

111
00:08:13,020 --> 00:08:14,460
You should let Xu Chengzhou replace you.

112
00:08:16,510 --> 00:08:17,510
Actually,

113
00:08:19,460 --> 00:08:21,340
I just want
to be with him for a while longer.

114
00:08:23,750 --> 00:08:24,510
If something happens,

115
00:08:25,070 --> 00:08:26,190
I'll call all of you.

116
00:08:26,900 --> 00:08:28,700
Xingruo, you must take care of yourself

117
00:08:28,700 --> 00:08:29,900
when you are alone.

118
00:08:46,690 --> 00:08:48,850
(Love House)

119
00:08:49,940 --> 00:08:50,990
Everything is damaged?

120
00:08:53,020 --> 00:08:53,900
All right. Thank you.

121
00:08:59,960 --> 00:09:00,630
Is everything all right?

122
00:09:00,800 --> 00:09:02,060
What did the insurance company say?

123
00:09:05,410 --> 00:09:06,940
They say the car
suffers from serious damage.

124
00:09:07,710 --> 00:09:10,260
They will compensate
according to the car damage

125
00:09:10,560 --> 00:09:12,230
after the traffic police's
accident report is released.

126
00:09:18,300 --> 00:09:18,900
What's wrong?

127
00:09:20,710 --> 00:09:22,590
I think this incident is strange.

128
00:09:22,590 --> 00:09:23,390
Don't you feel it?

129
00:09:24,140 --> 00:09:25,470
Zhai Jiajing borrowed the car from me.

130
00:09:25,710 --> 00:09:26,990
Right after she returned the car,

131
00:09:27,040 --> 00:09:28,660
Lu Xingyan had an accident
when he drove it.

132
00:09:29,830 --> 00:09:30,900
Zhai Jiajing?

133
00:09:30,990 --> 00:09:32,590
Why did she borrow the car from you?

134
00:09:34,870 --> 00:09:36,420
I still have something to tell you.

135
00:09:37,900 --> 00:09:39,300
I want to tell Shi Qin

136
00:09:39,300 --> 00:09:40,110
about us.

137
00:09:40,780 --> 00:09:42,390
I don't want her to misunderstand

138
00:09:42,390 --> 00:09:43,540
because of this.

139
00:09:44,780 --> 00:09:46,830
I will only tell Shi Qin.

140
00:09:47,990 --> 00:09:48,710
I believe

141
00:09:49,420 --> 00:09:51,180
she will never tell others.

142
00:09:54,180 --> 00:09:55,780
I'll ask you for one last time.

143
00:09:57,260 --> 00:09:58,540
Have you considered it thoroughly?

144
00:09:59,260 --> 00:10:00,140
I have.

145
00:10:11,140 --> 00:10:11,690
Fine.

146
00:10:12,660 --> 00:10:13,420
I understand.

147
00:10:14,750 --> 00:10:16,420
Can you do me one last favour?

148
00:10:20,060 --> 00:10:20,630
Tell me.

149
00:10:21,350 --> 00:10:23,110
I need to pick up a client
for the law firm.

150
00:10:23,590 --> 00:10:24,750
Can you lend me your car?

151
00:10:26,420 --> 00:10:29,180
Are you going to refuse me
for such a small favour?

152
00:10:42,470 --> 00:10:43,350
All right.

153
00:10:43,590 --> 00:10:45,780
We are all just assuming things.

154
00:10:46,420 --> 00:10:48,180
Let's talk when the police release

155
00:10:48,180 --> 00:10:49,520
the investigation report, all right?

156
00:10:50,350 --> 00:10:53,420
The whole car was burned to the ground.

157
00:10:54,060 --> 00:10:55,630
I'm afraid they won't find anything.

158
00:11:00,260 --> 00:11:00,900
Let's eat first.

159
00:11:26,770 --> 00:11:27,850
♪You♪

160
00:11:29,090 --> 00:11:30,530
♪Will you♪

161
00:11:32,090 --> 00:11:33,890
♪Think of me?♪

162
00:11:34,970 --> 00:11:37,050
♪Can it be♪

163
00:11:38,810 --> 00:11:39,930
♪Here?♪

164
00:11:40,890 --> 00:11:43,410
♪I could still see♪

165
00:11:43,930 --> 00:11:46,170
♪Your love for me♪

166
00:11:46,180 --> 00:11:47,510
Don't treat me as a client

167
00:11:48,180 --> 00:11:50,020
I hope you can
say anything on your mind

168
00:11:50,510 --> 00:11:51,940
when you are with me.

169
00:11:52,870 --> 00:11:53,660
Shen Xingruo!

170
00:11:54,140 --> 00:11:55,020
Lu Xingyan.

171
00:11:56,930 --> 00:11:59,090
♪I never let you go♪

172
00:11:59,780 --> 00:12:02,180
I will keep adjusting my perspective

173
00:12:02,240 --> 00:12:03,360
and think from another perspective

174
00:12:03,670 --> 00:12:05,360
to look at the problem
from your point of view.

175
00:12:06,930 --> 00:12:09,530
♪Want to find a way♪

176
00:12:09,540 --> 00:12:10,390
Are you all right?

177
00:12:10,990 --> 00:12:12,230
Emotional relationships

178
00:12:13,110 --> 00:12:14,230
and emotional stages

179
00:12:14,990 --> 00:12:16,710
are not important to me.

180
00:12:17,180 --> 00:12:17,940
Lu Xingyan.

181
00:12:20,110 --> 00:12:21,180
You are the only one I have.

182
00:12:21,710 --> 00:12:22,350
I am here.

183
00:12:31,900 --> 00:12:32,940
Lu Xingyan.

184
00:12:36,830 --> 00:12:40,540
I used to think

185
00:12:42,300 --> 00:12:44,830
that you would
take good care of yourself in the past.

186
00:12:47,900 --> 00:12:50,940
Even if we weren't together,

187
00:12:53,990 --> 00:12:56,020
you would also be well.

188
00:13:00,830 --> 00:13:01,870
Just now,

189
00:13:04,990 --> 00:13:07,830
when I got the informed consent,

190
00:13:09,180 --> 00:13:13,060
every article on it made me feel scared.

191
00:13:15,060 --> 00:13:17,300
I've never thought about

192
00:13:18,020 --> 00:13:20,510
you being so far away from me.

193
00:13:42,350 --> 00:13:43,630
Lu Xingyan.

194
00:13:47,300 --> 00:13:48,990
I beg you.

195
00:13:50,630 --> 00:13:52,470
Wake up.

196
00:14:28,630 --> 00:14:30,780
He hasn't woken up. It's me.

197
00:14:45,150 --> 00:14:47,140
Have you stayed here all night
without eating and drinking?

198
00:14:49,230 --> 00:14:50,350
I don't have any appetite.

199
00:14:50,990 --> 00:14:52,420
You should eat something.

200
00:14:53,660 --> 00:14:54,590
If this goes on,

201
00:14:55,290 --> 00:14:56,590
I'm not sure if he will wake up or not,

202
00:15:00,230 --> 00:15:01,350
but you might faint first.

203
00:15:03,260 --> 00:15:04,390
He will wake up.

204
00:15:21,350 --> 00:15:22,000
Then,

205
00:15:25,230 --> 00:15:26,260
you should go back and rest.

206
00:15:27,540 --> 00:15:28,710
I'll accompany him for one day.

207
00:15:29,870 --> 00:15:30,420
No need.

208
00:15:31,940 --> 00:15:33,350
I want to accompany him myself.

209
00:15:34,110 --> 00:15:35,870
I know
both of you love each other a lot.

210
00:15:39,180 --> 00:15:40,510
But how long have you been here?

211
00:15:41,650 --> 00:15:42,830
You haven't taken a bath for days.

212
00:15:44,060 --> 00:15:45,900
You need to take a bath
and come back at least.

213
00:15:50,020 --> 00:15:50,990
I've asked the doctor.

214
00:15:52,350 --> 00:15:54,020
Lu Xingyan's brain haemorrhage condition

215
00:15:54,020 --> 00:15:54,830
is under control.

216
00:15:55,940 --> 00:15:57,260
He will wake up soon.

217
00:15:59,110 --> 00:16:00,110
Do you want him

218
00:16:00,110 --> 00:16:01,530
to see how unkempt you look
when he wakes up?

219
00:16:08,140 --> 00:16:08,710
Don't worry.

220
00:16:10,710 --> 00:16:12,660
As soon as he wakes up,
I will tell you immediately.

221
00:16:23,540 --> 00:16:24,630
I'll go back to take a shower

222
00:16:25,390 --> 00:16:26,260
and return immediately.

223
00:16:33,260 --> 00:16:34,020
I'll leave

224
00:16:35,590 --> 00:16:36,630
Lu Xingyan in your hands.

225
00:17:08,140 --> 00:17:09,790
I wonder how is Xing now.

226
00:17:10,700 --> 00:17:11,790
Calm down.

227
00:17:11,790 --> 00:17:13,530
Are you still worried
when Xingruo is there with him?

228
00:17:13,590 --> 00:17:14,790
Hospitals now are so bad.

229
00:17:14,840 --> 00:17:16,230
They only let one person
accompany the patient.

230
00:17:16,240 --> 00:17:17,550
Otherwise, I'll also
go and accompany Xing.

231
00:17:19,740 --> 00:17:21,590
Xingruo, why are you back?

232
00:17:22,870 --> 00:17:23,980
I've come back to take a shower.

233
00:17:26,070 --> 00:17:26,660
Then...

234
00:17:27,310 --> 00:17:27,980
I'll go there now.

235
00:17:28,270 --> 00:17:28,870
No need.

236
00:17:29,500 --> 00:17:30,390
Don't worry.

237
00:17:30,550 --> 00:17:31,830
Yu Si is there.

238
00:17:32,270 --> 00:17:33,830
What? Yu Si?

239
00:17:34,310 --> 00:17:35,700
You let Yu Si accompany Xing?

240
00:17:35,700 --> 00:17:37,410
Aren't you afraid that he might
remove Xing's life support?

241
00:17:37,420 --> 00:17:38,230
I'll head over immediately.

242
00:17:39,350 --> 00:17:40,590
Calm down.

243
00:17:40,940 --> 00:17:42,900
It's the 21st Century now.

244
00:17:42,900 --> 00:17:44,550
People don't hurt someone
in broad daylight.

245
00:17:45,790 --> 00:17:47,180
I'm just worried about Xing.

246
00:17:47,550 --> 00:17:48,870
I know you are anxious.

247
00:17:49,310 --> 00:17:50,740
We will follow Xingruo's orders.

248
00:17:51,700 --> 00:17:52,830
Don't worry.

249
00:17:52,940 --> 00:17:53,980
He will be fine.

250
00:17:54,350 --> 00:17:55,500
I'll trouble you two again later.

251
00:17:55,700 --> 00:17:56,590
Go and rest for a while.

252
00:17:56,770 --> 00:17:57,460
I'm going upstairs.

253
00:18:04,220 --> 00:18:05,030
Lu Xingyan.

254
00:18:07,550 --> 00:18:08,630
Look what has happened to Xingruo

255
00:18:10,900 --> 00:18:12,870
because of you.

256
00:18:14,140 --> 00:18:14,660
I'm telling you.

257
00:18:17,870 --> 00:18:19,500
You better wake up immediately

258
00:18:20,700 --> 00:18:21,940
and give her a normal life.

259
00:18:25,830 --> 00:18:26,900
If you die like this,

260
00:18:29,110 --> 00:18:31,500
I'll bring Shen Xingruo
to Germany immediately.

261
00:18:32,590 --> 00:18:33,350
Do you hear me?

262
00:18:35,790 --> 00:18:36,660
Do you hear me?

263
00:18:53,270 --> 00:18:54,660
Thank you for taking care of him.

264
00:18:54,950 --> 00:18:55,800
Sorry for troubling you.

265
00:18:56,550 --> 00:18:57,980
Why don't you rest for a while?

266
00:18:58,420 --> 00:18:59,660
I couldn't stay put at home,

267
00:19:00,070 --> 00:19:02,790
so I thought about coming
to accompany him.

268
00:19:13,330 --> 00:19:16,290
(In-patient Department)

269
00:19:29,700 --> 00:19:30,500
Mr. Yu.

270
00:19:34,740 --> 00:19:35,350
Lawyer Zhai.

271
00:19:36,740 --> 00:19:37,940
Are you here to visit Lu Xingyan too?

272
00:19:38,900 --> 00:19:39,550
Yes.

273
00:19:40,350 --> 00:19:42,070
Xingruo has been busy in recent days.

274
00:19:42,070 --> 00:19:43,030
I came here to help her.

275
00:19:43,900 --> 00:19:44,550
Help her?

276
00:19:48,980 --> 00:19:50,700
I help Xingruo because I like her.

277
00:19:51,590 --> 00:19:53,390
Are you helping her
because you like someone?

278
00:19:56,180 --> 00:19:58,270
Mr. Yu, you are good at joking.

279
00:19:59,110 --> 00:20:01,030
Xingruo and I were classmates.

280
