609
00:37:48,350 --> 00:37:49,190
Sure.

610
00:38:11,390 --> 00:38:12,900
Turn around. Let me shave it for you.

611
00:38:57,940 --> 00:38:58,500
Don't laugh.

612
00:39:14,460 --> 00:39:15,060
Lift your chin.

613
00:39:20,350 --> 00:39:20,900
