615
00:39:29,350 --> 00:39:30,620
I was thinking.

616
00:39:31,900 --> 00:39:33,790
Back in the hospital,

617
00:39:34,830 --> 00:39:35,870
I thought

618
00:39:36,230 --> 00:39:37,940
I missed out on

619
00:39:37,940 --> 00:39:39,790
many opportunities to be with you

620
00:39:40,840 --> 00:39:41,630
so

621
00:39:42,390 --> 00:39:43,940
I want to make up

622
00:39:44,350 --> 00:39:46,390
