623
00:39:47,090 --> 00:39:48,410
♪Piece together♪

624
00:39:48,410 --> 00:39:52,330
♪Every scene of what we belonged♪

625
00:39:52,450 --> 00:39:54,130
♪How I wish in the future♪

626
00:39:54,370 --> 00:39:57,090
♪Longing could turn into
staying together forever♪

627
00:39:57,150 --> 00:39:57,790
What are you doing?

628
00:40:00,790 --> 00:40:02,540
Aren't you trying to make up

629
00:40:03,620 --> 00:40:05,230
