631
00:40:09,410 --> 00:40:11,610
♪Time pauses forever♪

632
00:40:11,610 --> 00:40:12,610
♪It turns out♪

633
00:40:12,610 --> 00:40:16,010
♪Every profound moment
is related to you♪

634
00:40:16,050 --> 00:40:18,770
♪From the beginning to the end♪

635
00:40:18,810 --> 00:40:19,650
♪It turns out♪

636
00:40:19,690 --> 00:40:23,170
♪You've always been a part of my life♪

637
00:40:23,210 --> 00:40:25,650
♪As if you've never left♪

638
00:40:25,690 --> 00:40:28,130
♪I still remember loving
each other deeply♪

639
00:40:28,210 --> 00:40:30,290
♪Searching for what you like♪

640
00:40:30,290 --> 00:40:32,850
♪Getting used to your habits♪

641
00:40:33,270 --> 00:40:34,820
Eat more.

